Privacy Policy for Caption Exporter

Effective Date: 11-19-2023

Welcome to the Caption Exporter Chrome extension. This privacy policy outlines our practices regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of information for users of the Caption Exporter.

1. Data Collection and Use

No Data Collection: Caption Exporter does not collect, store, or share any personal data of its users.
Local Data Processing: All data processing and storage occur locally on the user's device. No data is transmitted to remote servers or third parties.
2. User Control and Responsibility

User-Controlled Data: Users have complete control over their data. The extension does not access, retrieve, or manage user data beyond the scope of its functionality.
User Responsibility: Users are responsible for any actions they take while using the extension. By using Caption Exporter, users agree to use it at their own risk.
3. No Third-Party Data Sharing

No Sharing of Data: We do not share any data with third-party entities, as no user data is collected or stored by the extension.
4. Liability and Risk

Use at Own Risk: Users utilize the Caption Exporter extension at their own risk. We are not liable for any direct or indirect consequences arising from the use of the extension.
5. Consent

Acceptance of Terms: By using the Caption Exporter, users consent to this privacy policy and its terms.
6. Changes to the Privacy Policy

We reserve the right to modify this privacy policy at any time. Users are encouraged to review it periodically for any changes.
7. Contact Information

For any questions or concerns regarding this privacy policy, users can contact us through our listed support channels (if applicable).
Thank you for using Caption Exporter.
